      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... it's not just being lonely. it's like the version of me that existed with him is gone too. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like i'm just a shell moving through the rooms. how am i supposed to just \"reach out\" and talk about this when there's nothing left to talk about? the world just feels empty and hollow.",
